Dear cryptocolleages,

We are working in a new patent in order to use CD ROMS with random bits as
a one time pad key, in order to offer "perfect secret" on a cheap basis.  

Please let me know any device related with this one that you know, and if
anybody ask for the text of the patent we are working on, I shall be very
pleased sending it by post mail (sorry, at the moment, everything we have
is in Spanish).


